      • compareTo

        public int compareTo​(Lease l)
        Compares this lease to another lease for order. Leases are ordered according to start dates, then end dates(if the start dates are the same).
        Specified by:
        compareTo in interface java.lang.Comparable<Lease>
        Parameters:
        l - Lease being compared to
        Returns:
        A negative integer if the lease is less than l, 0 if they're of equal order, and a positive integer if its greater than l.
